OL,3,C2024 set to be hottest year on record,
OL,4,Ccapping a 'decade of deadly heat'
OL,6,FIn the past year, weather linked to
OL,7,Fclimate change has killed thousands
OL,8,Faround the world as temperatures
OL,9,Fincreased by 1.5 degrees for the first
OL,10,Ftime
OL,12,FThe past year is a set to be the
OL,13,Fhottest on record, capping a "decade
OL,14,Fof deadly heat", the UN has said.
OL,16,FIn his new year message, UN secretary-
OL,17,Fgeneral Antonio Guterres said the 10
OL,18,Fhottest years on record have happened
OL,19,Fin the last decade, including 2024.
