OL,3,C2024 set to be hottest year on record,
OL,4,Ccapping a 'decade of deadly heat'
OL,6,FMr Guterres said: "I can officially
OL,7,Freport that we have just endured a
OL,8,Fdecade of deadly heat.
OL,10,F"The top ten 10 hottest years on
OL,11,Frecord have happened in the last 10
OL,12,Fyears, including 2024.
OL,14,F"This is climate breakdown, in real
OL,15,Ftime. We must exit this road to ruin
OL,16,Fand we have no time to lose.
